<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ʿnduh ạ̉ml fy̱ã</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ʿndh ạ̉ml fyã wbytạ̉ny̱ wyṭwl bạlh ʿly
 mḥbth ly hy ạlly jạbtny lyh
 ʿndh ạ̉ml fy wf qlby qsạwẗ wf qlbh ḥnyẗ
 mạfysẖ mtẖạlh fy ʿṭfẗ wạlḥb ạlly fyh
 ạlly btʿmlh dạ ktyr yạ yswʿ yạ ḥbyby mạlksẖ
 nẓyr
 btqạbl sẖry bạlkẖyr
 ạlly btʿmlh dạ ktyr qlbk dạymaⁿạ ṭyb wkbyr
 wbtrḥm ḍʿfy yạ qdyr
 ạlḥb dạ klh hạlạqyh fyn gẖyr ʿndk
 qlby ạ̹nt ḥyạth ạ̹nt ạlly bạqwl lh ạ̉nạ ʿmry
 klh lyk
 ạ̉nạ qlby fạḍl lh ḥbh whynṭq ạsmh mʿ dqạth
 wmsẖ hạfrṭ fyk mạ ṣdqt ạ̉lạqyk</lyrics>
